    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the unknown with Rake Remastered, a spiritual successor to the haunting 2015 classic. Dive into the heart of an unforgiving wilderness where danger lurks in every shadow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As an investigator, you're drawn to a forest shrouded in mystery, tasked with uncovering the truth behind a string of chilling disappearances. Armed with only a handful of tools, you must navigate the eerie landscape, piece together unsettling clues, and face a predator unlike anything you've encountered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The forest holds its secrets close, and the line between hunter and hunted grows thinner with every passing moment. Will you survive the night, or will the Rake claim you as its next victim?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The answers are out there. But at what cost?</p>",
